Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: why am i single
des:
If you’re currently single or in a relationship, it may feel like the whole scene is one big guessing game sometimes.
 
"When should you go on a date?" or "What should you do on your date?" 

You've got to know that there are energies at play here, and Why am I Single? skill will intuitively guide you in your True Love's direction.

If this sounds like what you need, then it's time to meet Miss Moon, who will guide you on your quest for True Love.

She is your true girlfriend.

This is a free forecast based on the energies of the current Moon phase and your current Menstrual Cycle*.

With Why Am I Single?, Miss Moon is always there for you when you need those deep and meaningful insights.

For best results, use on a weekly basis.

To find out more, go to www.whyamisinglethegame.com
 
* The Menstrual Cycle calculator in the skill is an approximation forecast only.
